data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Port St. Lucie! This 4-bed, 2-bath gem near the Turnpike promises convenience and peace of mind. The ideal floor plan connects a custom kitchen to inviting living spaces, perfect for entertaining. This home has a 2018 roof, 2020 AC, reverse osmosis system, ensuring worry-free living--no need for storm concerns or insurance issues. This home has been meticulously maintained since being built, and it in excellent move in ready condition with build quality you will not see in new construction homes today. Step outside to a huge private yard, ideal for outdoor activities and relaxation, this home is perfect for every occasion. This haven offers convenience, style, and worry-free living. Don't miss out--schedule a viewing today and make it yours!
